The paper deals with the problem of document retrieval, which is a core topic in information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of indexes and data structures to efficiently solve the problem, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of external memory models, which is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC) and parallel computing (cs.CC).
